    • signal

      public void signal(int marks, String feedback)
      Signals test results (marks and feedback) to the attached observer.

      This method invokes the update method on the attached observer with the given marks, feedback, and the name of the class signaling the results.

      Specified by:
      signal in interface TestSubject
      Parameters:
      marks - the marks obtained for the test.
      feedback - the feedback provided for the test.
